  <steps>
    <step order="0" name="Context Check + Rigor Declaration">"🔒 RIGOR LEVEL: FULL — Chat factory hot path; privacy filter; ADR-015 binding."</step>
    <step order="1" name="Review Progress">Read TASK-INDEX; confirm 053 + 073 complete.</step>
    <step order="2" name="Gather Resources">Read SprkChatAgentFactory + workspace state service + serialized state interface.</step>
    <step order="3" name="Refine Workspace State Block Builder">Replace minimal text summary from task 053 with rich serialized-state composition. Filter: `visibleToAssistant: true` AND widget has impl.</step>
    <step order="4" name="Format for Prompt">Each tab's visible state as structured block (JSON or table-like format the LLM can parse).</step>
    <step order="5" name="Budget Enforcement">Respect 8K via shared budget tracker (task 068).</step>
    <step order="6" name="Tests">Unit tests: (a) visible + impl → in prompt; (b) visible + no impl → not in prompt; (c) not visible → not in prompt; (d) budget enforcement.</step>
    <step order="7" name="Integration Test">End-to-end: 3 tabs (visible+impl, visible+no-impl, not-visible); verify only first appears in agent prompt.</step>
    <step order="8" name="Publish-Size + CVE">dotnet publish + vulnerable check.</step>
    <step order="9.5" name="Quality Gates (FULL)">code-review + adr-check (ADR-010/013/015/029).</step>
